00:20:08.840 --> 00:20:12.330
that has been influenced
by legislation,

00:20:12.330 --> 00:20:15.480
how it's been influenced
by just the experience

00:20:15.480 --> 00:20:19.300
of the Vietnam Veterans
Memorial.

00:20:19.300 --> 00:20:23.620
And then from Kristin and
