00:37:00.870 --> 00:37:03.240
But in addition to
reading the report

00:37:03.240 --> 00:37:05.880
of the monument avenue
commission in Richmond,

00:37:05.880 --> 00:37:09.820
I recommend to you that you read
Mitchell Andrew's book recently

00:37:09.820 --> 00:37:13.200
came out about his decision
and the decision in New Orleans

00:37:13.200 --> 00:37:16.080
to remove the confederate
statues.

00:37:16.080 --> 00:37:19.720
So you have one mayor, a
white mayor in New Orleans,

00:37:19.720 --> 00:37:22.700
removing the symbols
of white supremacy.

00:37:22.700 --> 00:37:24.650
You have an African
American mayor

00:37:24.650 --> 00:37:27.900
in Richmond endorsing
a preservation

00:37:27.900 --> 00:37:30.460
of Civil War monuments.

00:37:30.460 --> 00:37:32.990
So we've got very
interesting conversation going

00:37:32.990 --> 00:37:34.960
on here in those two cities.

00:37:34.960 --> 00:37:38.950
And I will add to that
where I went to school

00:37:38.950 --> 00:37:41.010
